  pekko-actor  for Pekko jar dependencies, the groupId is &ldquo;org.apache.pekko&rdquo; instead of &ldquo;com.typesafe.akka&rdquo; the jar names start with &ldquo;pekko&rdquo; instead of &ldquo;akka&rdquo; - e.g. pekko-actor_2.13.jar instead of akka-actor_2.13.jar Alpakka equivalent is &ldquo;pekko-connectors&rdquo; - e.g. pekko-connectors-kafka_2.13.jar instead of alpakka-kafka_2.13.jar Pekko packages start with &ldquo;org.apache.pekko&rdquo; instead of &ldquo;akka&rdquo; - e.g. import org.apache.pekko.actor instead of import akka.actor Where class names have &ldquo;Akka&rdquo; in the name, the Pekko ones have &ldquo;Pekko&rdquo; - e.g. PekkoException instead of AkkaException Config names use &ldquo;pek
