tive-image module exports and old TypedActor tests must be avoided.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"If generated tests exercise org.apache.pekko.io.dns.DnsSettings or default DNS fallback behavior, keep/add the JVM and native-image argument `--add-exports=java.base/sun.net.dns=ALL-UNNAMED`, because the artifact still reflectively reaches `sun.net.dns.ResolverConfiguration` on JDK 9+. Do not use `org.apache.pekko.actor.TypedActor`, `TypedActorExtension`, or `TypedProps` for 2.0.0-M1; those classes are present in 1.1.5 but absent from the 2.0.0-M1 jar. Use remaining classic actor APIs such as `ActorSystem`, `Props`, serialization, configuration, and reflective dynamic-access paths for coverage.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Copying the existing 1.1.5 TypedActor tests or metadata into 2.0.0-M1 will fail compilation because the classes were removed.\",\n    \"Pekko TestKit is documented as an optional test dependency for actor testing, but it is not required before meaningful core pekko-actor coverage is reachable; add it only if generated tests intentionally use TestKit APIs.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02a8d516a83aaeaa016a422a1848a081948a0f1a257a9ad7bf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1201, "output": 803, "cacheRead": 27648, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29652, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782721039696, "responseId": "resp_02a8d516a83aaeaa016a422a1053c48194834039db5d731e32"}}
